<p><big><b><a href="/wiki/Scapular" title="Scapular">Scapular</a></b></big><br /></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="/wiki/File:Escapulariocafe.JPG" class="image" title="Escapulariocafe.JPG"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/73/Escapulariocafe.JPG/100px-Escapulariocafe.JPG" width="100" height="72" border="0" /></a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="font-size:15px">
<p><br />
<b>General articles</b><br />
<a href="/wiki/St._Simon_Stock" title="St. Simon Stock" class="mw-redirect">St. Simon Stock</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Our_Lady_of_Mount_Carmel" title="Our Lady of Mount Carmel">Our Lady of Mt. Carmel</a><br />
