<p><b>Specific Scapulars</b><br />
<a href="/wiki/Brown_Scapular" title="Brown Scapular" class="mw-redirect">Mount Carmel (Brown)</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Fivefold_Scapular" title="Fivefold Scapular">Fivefold Scapular</a><br />
