</div>
<p><a name="External_links" id="External_links"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Sacred_Heart&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=XIcEAAAAQAAJ&amp;pg=PR1&amp;dq=1863+croiset" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=XIcEAAAAQAAJ&amp;pg=PR1&amp;dq=1863+croiset" rel="nofollow">Devotion to the Sacred Heart of Jesus, which was commanded to be written by Jesus Himself through St. Margaret Mary</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.newadvent.org/cathen/07163a.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.newadvent.org/cathen/07163a.htm" rel="nofollow"><i>Devotion to the Sacred Heart of Jesus</i></a>, from <a href="/wiki/Catholic_Encyclopedia" title="Catholic Encyclopedia">Catholic Encyclopedia</a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.roman-catholic-prayers.com/prayer/sacred_heart.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.roman-catholic-prayers.com/prayer/sacred_heart.htm" rel="nofollow">The <i>Sacred Heart Prayer</i></a>.</li>
<li>Catholic <a href="http://www.sistersofcarmel.com/devotion-to-the-sacred-heart-of-jesus.php" class="external text" title="http://www.sistersofcarmel.com/devotion-to-the-sacred-heart-of-jesus.php" rel="nofollow"><i>Devotion to the Sacred Heart of Jesus</i></a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.sticna.com/consecration_to_the_Hearts_of_Jesus_and_Mary.html" class="external text" title="http://www.sticna.com/consecration_to_the_Hearts_of_Jesus_and_Mary.html" rel="nofollow"><i>What is consecration and commitment to the hearts of Jesus and Mary</i></a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://our.homewithgod.com/sacredheart/" class="external text" title="http://our.homewithgod.com/sacredheart/" rel="nofollow">The Life of Saint Margaret Mary in her own words</a>.</li>
</ul>


